## 🇬🇧 Privacy Policy (English)

**Privacy Policy for VÄND10: Neon Palace**  

Omerion Studios AB ("we", "us", or "our") respects your privacy. This policy explains how we handle personal information in relation to our app **VÄND10: Neon Palace**.

### Information Collection
The app does not collect any personally identifiable information. The game runs entirely locally on your device.  

### Third-Party Services
We may use third-party services (such as analytics or ads) in the future. If that happens, this policy will be updated accordingly.  

### Security
We take reasonable measures to protect your information. Since the app does not collect data, the risk of exposure is very low.  

### Contact
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:  
📧 **omerionstudiosab@gmail.com**  
🌐 [www.omerionstudios.com](http://www.omerionstudios.com)  
